On the Handling Unit card you can edit the content by pressing **Actions->Edit Contents**:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000424-0/6HandlingUnitsManagement.png"><br><br>


A journal will open in which you can enter items to be assigned to the unit:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000424-0/8HandlingUnitsManagement.png"><br>

on the lines you indicate the item, location, bin and quantity and then you can post.

<br>

Now, returning to the handling unit tab, you will find the item added to the handling unit content.


<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000424-0/9HandlingUnitsManagement.png"><br>